                <p class="text-sm text-[#777] mb-3">For fully learned controllers (RL, imitation learning, VLA) where behavior emerges from neural nets with no explicit code, the NeuralActionGate sits between action output and motor execution — checking every action against conscience.exe rules and body.api safety envelope at 200Hz+. Deny dominates. Actions exceeding safety bounds are clamped to the nearest safe value. Every evaluation is logged.</p>
